				<p><p>Scope showed data being sent to the robot.  I discovered the console was enabled on the raspberry pi 3 and disabled it; the problem is now resolved.</p>

<p>Specifically, run the following commands<BR>
sudo systemctl stop serial-getty@ttyS0.service<BR>
sudo systemctl disable serial-getty@ttyS0.service<BR></p>

<p>Then edit /boot/cmdline.txt and remove the following option from the file</p>

<p>console=serial0,115200<BR></p>

<p>Save and reboot.  For more information see 
<a href="http://spellfoundry.com/2016/05/29/configuring-gpio-serial-port-raspbian-jessie-including-pi-3/" rel="nofollow noreferrer">http://spellfoundry.com/2016/05/29/configuring-gpio-serial-port-raspbian-jessie-including-pi-3/</a></p>
